articles.title: Venezuela releases jailed Americans in deal that frees migrants deported to El Salvador by US
articles.description: Venezuela has released jailed Americans in an agreement that involves the release of migrants deported to El Salvador by the U.S. [2, 3].

articles.title: Trump sues Wall Street Journal and media mogul Rupert Murdoch over reporting on Epstein ties
